uiConfig.queryString: Type = com.oraclecloud.identityControlPlane.CreateUser | fields -Entity, 'User Name', Event, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source' | timestats count
Type in (com.oraclecloud.identitycontrolplane.removeuserfromgroup, com.oraclecloud.identitycontrolplane.addusertogroup) and Method != get | timestats count
Type like '%resetpassword%' and Message like '%succeeded%' | fields -'Log Source', -Label, -'Problem Priority', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Entity Type', -Entity, Service | timestats span = 1day count

Type = com.oraclecloud.IdentitySignOn.InteractiveLogin and Status != '200' | fields -Entity, 'User Name', Event, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source' | timestats span = 1day count
Type like 'com.oraclecloud.identitycontrolplane%identityprovider' and Method != get | timestats count

Type in (com.oraclecloud.identitycontrolplane.deactivateuser, com.oraclecloud.identitycontrolplane.deleteuser, com.oraclecloud.identitycontrolplane.updateuser, com.oraclecloud.identitycontrolplane.updateusercapabilities, com.oraclecloud.identitycontrolplane.updateuserstate, com.oraclecloud.identityprovisioning.updateuseruipassword) and Method != get and 'Log Source' = 'OCI Audit Logs' and 'User Name' != 'identity-soup' | timestats count
Type = com.oraclecloud.identityControlPlane.UploadApiKey | fields -Entity, 'User Name', Event, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source' | timestats count

Type like '%identity%' and 'User Name' != 'identity-soup' and Principal not like '%cloudguard%' and 'User Agent String' not like 'cloud-infra/%' and 'User Agent String' not like 'cloud infra%' | eval 'User Name' = if('User Name' = 'null', 'Unknown User', 'User Name') | stats count as logrecords by 'User Name'
Type like '%identity%policy%' and Method != get | fields -Entity, 'User Name', Event, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source' | timestats count
Type = com.oraclecloud.IdentitySignOn.InteractiveLogin and Status = '200' | stats latest(Time) as 'Last Login' by 'User Name' | where 'Last Login' < dateRelative(30day)

Type = com.oraclecloud.IdentitySignOn.InteractiveLogin and Status = '200' | fields -Entity, 'User Name', Event, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source' | timestats span = 1day count
Type like '%identity%idpgroup%' and Method != get | fields -Entity, 'User Name', Event, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source' | timestats count
